{"tid":800819,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Freelance 先係香港最理想的生活。","createTime":"2018-08-31T07:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T08:19:00.000Z","uid":193600,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ac8c3b83dc36831d288b2bf4416f6eff8d0b99fb","tid":800819,"uid":193600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:21:51.000Z","msg":"我2X歲 以前做政府，近年幾出來做自由職業者。<br />\n<br />\n雖然自由業但同以前差唔多忙，但叫做搵番生命的意義，每日都過得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n星期六日固定有booking 要做野，平日時間無Job 就係自己的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵得唔算多，淡季每月2萬鬆的，旺季6-7萬，平均三萬中。因為慣左慳，而且對食、衣著無咩要求，所以駛得好少，每個月開支都係$4000左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，比完家用後都叫貯到的錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平日就係訓到9點，然後起身寫下野，睇下書，無野做就睇下電影，去到下午茶時間就去吉仔食個Tea 玩下電話，夜晚就做Gym 做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前座Office 肥左少少，而家Fit 到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有人問我會唔會出番來做全職，我話暫時唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始都比人話佛系唔上進，不過真係捱過朝9晚6唔駛Ot時番學校讀master ,呢的日子真係辛苦到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日十點幾番到屋企訓一陣又要番工無限Loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家日日看人趕頭趕命逼地鐵🚇，家下看透世事在吉仔談笑風生，呢的先係人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有個做醫院的女朋友，搵多我皮幾野一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一樣都係慳妹，freelance 之後仲多左時間同她拍拖旅行，真係覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果香港樓價唔係甘X高，我一定係Top1%的快樂人生，而家都唔差，Top 5%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開心唔係搵幾多錢買幾多奢侈品，而係有時間做自己中意既野、陪親愛既人，同時唔駛為錢煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e685dde34215db17a4a19df3da80649bc1b45bb","tid":800819,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:27:53.000Z","msg":"3/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019ac09a9e80e445240b2c98a4f6c01199bf532a","tid":800819,"uid":202254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"Ching 你邊方面free lance"},{"pid":"2cf6f02edbf772614dc0c39ebf72a401aa7b9270","tid":800819,"uid":48800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:50:51.000Z","msg":"屌你啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：文員仔一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff83259218f2acd043017ba630f0a767975ede6f","tid":800819,"uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:00:14.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"aecd3266d308c39ec8f667fbb99575c2b5a002ec","tid":800819,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 🍇"},{"pid":"09bb4f7101ce35b0501832eec174d5d8b3bb325a","tid":800819,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"又層壓搵下線...."},{"pid":"25904f3c5c289549ef640b6e9c2356c902e43fb5","tid":800819,"uid":50504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"睇黎巴打都搵夠啦,想益下其他人"}]}